item.text: ALL QUESTIONS CONTAINED IN THIS QUESTIONNAIRE ARE OPTIONAL AND WILL BE KEPT STRICTLY CONFIDENTIAL.

extension.valueString: Please answer Yes or No to each of the following questions:

valueCodeableConcept.text: A control where choices are listed with a button beside them. The button can be toggled to select or de-select a given choice. Selecting one item deselects all others.

item.text: Are you pregnant? (enableWhen = gender is Female)
Are you diabetic? (enableWhen = gender is Female)
Have you been diagnosed with Gestational Diabetes? (enableBehavior = only when pregnant and diabetic)
Have you had mammogram before?(enableWhenExpression = only when gender is female and age > 40)

valueCodeableConcept.text: A control where an axis is displayed between the high and low values and the control can be visually manipulated to select a value anywhere on the axis.
